title: Stylish Prompts Logo
prompt: A modern logo design with the words Stylish Prompts in a smooth cursive font. The text has a vibrant gradient color blend from orange to pink to purple. The background is solid black, making the colorful gradient text stand out. The overall look should be elegant, minimal, and eye-catching.

title: Pirate Banana at Tajmahal
prompt: A banana character dressed in a full pirate costume (hat, eyepatch, coat, and sword), standing proudly in front of the Taj Mahal. The Taj Mahal should be clearly visible in the background, with realistic lighting and detail. The scene should be colorful.
